name: Custom Diaper Spot
description: This listing is to purchase one custom diaper slot. Please choose the diaper option you would like for me to make. Pricing is as follows: OS Pocket (snaps or aplix) w/o insert $14 OS Pocket (snaps or aplix) w/ bamboo/hemp prefold $16 OS Swim Diaper (snaps or aplix) $14 OS AI2 (snaps or aplix) $20 OS AIO (snaps or aplix) $25 OS Fitted (snapped or snapless) $26, $24 NB Fitted $14 ***If you will be sending me fabric for your diaper please use code "SYOF" at checkout.*** I will email the Google Docs form for fabrics and other options pertaining to your custom diaper to the email you provide at checkout. The diapers pictured are examples of past creations and are no longer for sale at this time. The diaper you will receive will be 100% hand made by me in my home to your specifications. You can also see more of my creations here on facebook: https://www.facebook.com/media/albums/?id=266907196662855
